'''''Star Wars at 30''''' was a live program broadcast on [[Wikipedia:G4 (TV channel)|G4]] that highlighted the events of [[Celebration IV]] and the history of Star Wars. It was broadcast on [[May 25]], [[2007]], the thirtieth anniversary of the release of [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']]. The program featured appearances by [[Amy Allen]], [[Ray Park]], [[Temuera Morrison]], [[Peter Mayhew]], and many others.

